author: Rossmallow

changelog.release_notes: A WatchApp that displays the Information Resource Center capacity data for District 219 high schools, North and West. On the title screen press the up button to get Niles North's information, or press down to get Niles West's information. On either of the information pages press the center button to refresh the information show, and press back to return to the title screen. https://github.com/Rossmallow/D219-IRC-Capacity-WatchApp/blob/master/src/app.js v1.0
